10. License violation
   
   Any violation of the terms of this license automatically terminates 
   your rights under it. Upon termination, you must cease all use, 
   distribution, and modification of the Software.

   However, your rights are automatically reinstated if you cure the 
   violation within 30 days after becoming aware of it, provided this 
   is your first violation received from the copyright holder(s).

   For subsequent or uncured violations, rights may be reinstated by 
   the copyright holder(s) in writing.

