Platform telemetry: Telemetry, analytics, or diagnostic data collected 
at the operating system level by the platform provider (e.g., iOS, Android) 
and outside the direct control of the Software's author is outside the 
scope of clause 5(a). This license governs only telemetry mechanisms 
implemented within the Software itself.